title: Leaves from the journal of our life in the Highlands, from 1848 to 1861.
author: Victoria
snippet: We passed close to Fettercaim, Sir J. Forbes'shouse ; then, farther on to the left, Fasque, belonging to Sir T. Gladstone, who has evidentlydone a great deal for the country, haAdng builtmany good cottages.
